oakcurric:unit-2866
  a curric:Unit ;
  rdfs:label "Refugees in France: reflexive verbs"@en ;
  curric:slug "refugees-in-france-reflexive-verbs" ;
  rdfs:comment """In this unit, reflexive -er verbs and pronouns are introduced in singular forms,
  and direct object pronouns revisited. New high frequency verbs are introduced to support
  discussion refugees in France."""@en ;
  curric:whyThisWhyNow """In this unit, pupils embed their knowledge of the present tense, extending
  it to include reflexive -er verbs and pronouns in singular persons. Revisiting this in the
  context of refugees in France gives pupils the opportunity to apply known vocabulary in less
  familiar contexts and to appreciate how this gives access to more advanced content, more
  complex texts and richer productive tasks.""" ;
  curric:hasPriorKnowledgeRequirement
    oakcurric:priorknowledge-2866-1 ,
    oakcurric:priorknowledge-2866-2 ,
    oakcurric:priorknowledge-2866-3 ,
    oakcurric:priorknowledge-2866-4 ;
  curric:id "2866"^^xsd:positiveInteger;
  dcterms:modified "2026-06-07T15:29:24.711678Z"^^xsd:dateTime ;
  curric:isUnitOf
    natcurric:scheme-languages-key-stage-3 ;
  curric:includesThread
    oakcurric:thread-the-present .

oakcurric:unit-2860
  a curric:Unit ;
  rdfs:label "Winter celebrations: present tense, adjectives, comparatives, partitive"@en ;
  curric:slug "winter-celebrations-present-tense-adjectives-comparatives-partitive" ;
  rdfs:comment """In this unit, based mainly on the present tense, pupils refresh their knowledge of
  adjective positioning, comparatives, and the use of de as partitive article and after
  expressions of quantity."""@en ;
  curric:whyThisWhyNow """In this unit, pupils anchor their knowledge of present tense verbs and
  consolidate knowledge of 'de' as they read about Christmas celebrations around the world.
  They apply their knowledge of comparative adjectives and adverbs and later in the unit, bring
  this all together in extended speaking on winter holidays.""" ;
  curric:hasPriorKnowledgeRequirement
    oakcurric:priorknowledge-2860-1 ,
    oakcurric:priorknowledge-2860-2 ,
    oakcurric:priorknowledge-2860-3 ,
